docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  README.md,project,JSONL lossless interchange contract
close_reason: "Rich JSONL persistence is lossless through the real installed package; unit, doctor, audit, package, and changelog gates pass."
body: "## Context\\n\\nProject management is context management. JSONL is the lossless interchange format, so dropping context during persistence violates its core contract.\\n\\n## Design\\n\\nUse SDK-registered namespaced item fields for source metadata that cannot safely overwrite pm reserved audit fields, then map them back to stable public JSONL keys on export."
